format_where

{% raw %} 
assert_and_print(
    format_where(
        "WHERE brand = 'my_brand'"
    ), "WHERE  brand = 'my_brand'"
)

format_sql

{% raw %} 
assert_and_print(
    format_sql("SELECT brand FROM table WHERE brand = 'my_brand'"),
"""
SELECT brand
FROM   table
WHERE  brand = 'my_brand'
""".strip()
)

SELECT brand
FROM   table
WHERE  brand = 'my_brand'
